text: Thirty Three () is a 1965 Soviet comedy movie directed by Georgiy Daneliya.В китайском Пинъяо прошла ретроспектива советского киноТРИДЦАТЬ ТРИ (1965) It stars Yevgeny Leonov, Nonna Mordyukova, and Lyubov Sokolova. ==Actors== * Yevgeny Leonov as Ivan Travkin * Nonna Mordyukova as Galina Pristyazhnyuk * Lyubov Sokolova as Travkin's wife * Viktor Avdyushko as Misha * Saveliy Kramarov as Rodion Homutov * Gennadi Yalovich as Scheremetyev == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Russian comedy movies Category:1965 comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Georgiy Daneliya Category:Soviet comedy movies
title: Thirty Three (movie)
